# Deployment

- Staging: branch `develop` → `jobtracker-staging.baseer.co.uk` / `jobtracker-api-staging.baseer.co.uk`
- Production: tag `v*` → `jobtracker.baseer.co.uk` / `jobtracker-api.baseer.co.uk`
- R2: `docket-documents-staging` / `docket-documents` — never public; presigned URLs only via `lib/r2.ts`
- Cookie domain must match app host (`jobtracker.baseer.co.uk` / `jobtracker-staging.baseer.co.uk`) for Pages/Workers session sharing
- Document ops in `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` and `docs/RUNBOOK.md`
